sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / kubectl
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Webhook as Webhook Server<br/>9443/TCP TLS
    participant ISCtrl as InferenceService<br/>Reconciler
    participant LLMCtrl as LLMInferenceService<br/>Reconciler
    participant GWCtrl as Gateway<br/>Reconciler
    participant NIMCtrl as NIM Account<br/>Reconciler
    participant CMCtrl as ConfigMap<br/>Reconciler
    participant SecCtrl as Secret<br/>Reconciler
    participant NVIDIA as NVIDIA NGC API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant ModelReg as Model Registry<br/>HTTP/HTTPS
    participant Dashboard as RHOAI Dashboard
    participant ServingAPI as model-serving-api<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over User,SecCtrl: Flow 1: InferenceService Deployment
    User->>K8sAPI: POST InferenceService<br/>Auth: User token
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: Mutate/Validate<br/>TLS (admission cert)
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Admission Response
    K8sAPI-->>User: InferenceService Created
    K8sAPI->>ISCtrl: Watch Event (ISVC)
    ISCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create OpenShift Route<br/>Auth: SA token
    ISCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create ClusterRoleBinding<br/>Auth: SA token
    ISCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create ServiceMonitor<br/>Auth: SA token
    ISCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create NetworkPolicy<br/>Auth: SA token
    ISCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create KEDA TriggerAuth<br/>Auth: SA token
    ISCtrl->>ModelReg: Sync model metadata<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    ModelReg-->>ISCtrl: Model labels/annotations

    Note over User,SecCtrl: Flow 2: NIM Account Provisioning
    User->>K8sAPI: POST NIM Account<br/>Auth: User token
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: Validate (singleton)<br/>TLS (admission cert)
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Admission Response
    K8sAPI->>NIMCtrl: Watch Event (Account)
    NIMCtrl->>NVIDIA: POST authn.nvidia.com<br/>Auth: Basic Auth (API key)
    NVIDIA-->>NIMCtrl: NGC Token
    NIMCtrl->>NVIDIA: GET api.ngc.nvidia.com<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (NGC)
    NVIDIA-->>NIMCtrl: Runtime catalog + model data
    NIMCtrl->>NVIDIA: HEAD nvcr.io manifest<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    NVIDIA-->>NIMCtrl: Image validation
    NIMCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create ConfigMap<br/>Auth: SA token
    NIMCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create OpenShift Template<br/>Auth: SA token
    NIMCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create Pull Secret<br/>Auth: SA token

    Note over User,SecCtrl: Flow 3: Gateway Authentication Bootstrap
    K8sAPI->>GWCtrl: Watch Event (Gateway)
    GWCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create EnvoyFilter<br/>(Authorino TLS termination)<br/>Auth: SA token
    GWCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create AuthPolicy<br/>(Kuadrant authentication)<br/>Auth: SA token

    Note over User,SecCtrl: Flow 4: CA Certificate Aggregation
    K8sAPI->>CMCtrl: Watch Event (odh-trusted-ca-bundle)
    K8sAPI->>CMCtrl: Watch Event (openshift-service-ca.crt)
    CMCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create/Update<br/>odh-kserve-custom-ca-bundle<br/>Auth: SA token
    CMCtrl->>K8sAPI: Delete storage-config<br/>(force regeneration)<br/>Auth: SA token

    Note over Dashboard,ServingAPI: Flow 5: Gateway Discovery (Dashboard)
    Dashboard->>ServingAPI: GET /api/v1/gateways<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (user)
    ServingAPI->>K8sAPI: SelfSubjectAccessReview<br/>(impersonated user check)
    K8sAPI-->>ServingAPI: RBAC result
    ServingAPI->>K8sAPI: List Gateways<br/>Auth: SA token
    K8sAPI-->>ServingAPI: Gateway resources
    ServingAPI-->>Dashboard: Filtered Gateway listeners
